<template>
    <router-view />
</template>
<script>
    if ('serviceWorker' in navigator) {
        window.addEventListener('load', () => {
            navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js').then(reg => {
                console.log('SW registered:', reg);
            }).catch(err => {
                console.error('SW registration failed:', err);
            });
        });
    }
</script>
